net.openhft.fix.include.util

Class FixConfig

  • java.lang.Object
    • net.openhft.fix.include.util.FixConfig
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Cloneable

    public class FixConfig
extends Object
implements Cloneable
    Default configuration class for a Fix 4.2 message. Uses static methods to initialize FIX 4.2 header and fields. The main purpose of this class is to initialize standard fix 4.2 fields to allocate memory before usage to avoid dynamic allocation of ByteBufferBytes during runtime for FIX fields data.
